OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNichols' lawyer calls for  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Furgent police reform       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The lawyer representing Tyre Nichols'  
OL,6, family has called on the US Congress to
OL,7, pass urgent police reform legislation  
OL,8, in the wake of his death.              
OL,10,FMr Nichols, 29, was fatally beaten by  
OL,11,Ffive police officers in January.       
OL,13,FSpeaking to US media, Ben Crump urged  
OL,14,FPresident Joe Biden to use Mr Nichols's
OL,15,Fdeath to gain support for the George   
OL,16,FFloyd Justice in Policing Act.         
OL,18,FAnd he said Mr Nichols's mother was    
OL,19,Fcoping her son's loss by hoping that   
OL,20,Fhis death could lead to change.        
